://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6643726021527911, \"rank\": 0.35105792818989034, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a gap between these squads, but Team USA needs to execute to make sure they defeat their northern rivals should they meet at this summer's Olympics.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6445682992702308e-26, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of Canada's biggest problems at the Olympics is its strength of schedule.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6643726021527911, \"rank\": 0.35105792818989034, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Led by new Brooklyn Nets head coach Jordi Fernandez, Canada has been drawn into Group A, also known as the Group of Death.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brooklyn_Nets\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0629162797521498e-73, \"text\": \"Brooklyn Nets\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brooklyn_Nets\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brooklyn_Nets\"}, {\"begin\": 1878, \"end\": 1884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6643726021527911, \"rank\": 0.35105792818989034, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroBasket_2009\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1586549000493311e-29, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroBasket_2009\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroBasket_2009\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's them, Spain, Greece, and Australia.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All four teams expect to compete for a medal here, maybe not gold, but all are worthy of grabbing the bronze.\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada is prone to stinkers.\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6643726021527911, \"rank\": 0.35105792818989034, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They lost an ugly game to Brazil at the 2023 FIBA World Cup and are capable of dropping one in group play.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2154, \"end\": 2160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999985848262, \"rank\": 1.4151083093055808e-09, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every single group game they have will be a dog fight meaning by the time they face Team USA, they could be running out of gas.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6445682992702308e-26, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The talent is there for Canada, but plenty of obstacles stand in their way and they will need an A+ performance if they are to take down Team USA for the second summer in a row.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2388, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6643726021527911, \"rank\": 0.35105792818989034, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6445682992702308e-26, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada's road to gold will begin against Giannis Antetokounmpo and Greece on Saturday, July 27.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2542, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour