 [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannes_Voigtmann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannes_Voigtmann\"}, {\"begin\": 6723, \"end\": 6740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannes_Thiemann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Johannes Thiemann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannes_Thiemann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannes_Thiemann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Head coach Gordon Herbert knows how to optimize this group and when they are at their best, they should be feared.\", \"from\": 6789, \"to\": 6903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6800, \"end\": 6814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_Herbert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gordon Herbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_Herbert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_Herbert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany will open their Olympic tournament against Rui Hachimura and Japan on Saturday, July 27.\", \"from\": 6905, \"to\": 7001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6905, \"end\": 6912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.673947957810241e-13, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 6960, \"end\": 6969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_Hachimura\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hachimura\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_Hachimura\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_Hachimura\"}, {\"begin\": 6974, \"end\": 6979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6263151754411918, \"rank\": 0.4861130850565483, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will also face France and Brazil in group play.\", \"from\": 7002, \"to\": 7054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7022, \"end\": 7028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9901787418083507e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7033, \"end\": 7039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999985848262, \"rank\": 1.4151083093055808e-09, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is one reason Greece is on this list: Giannis Antetokounmpo, the Greek Freak, the one-man fastbreak, could maybe push his team to a gold medal.\", \"from\": 7056, \"to\": 7205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7076, \"end\": 7082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999023220939736, \"rank\": 9.768744794159763e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7100, \"end\": 7121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giannis Antetokounmpo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giannis_Antetokounmpo\"}, {\"begin\": 7127, \"end\": 7132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999960265565093, \"rank\": 3.973459220854419e-06, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's highly unlikely, he's the only NBA player they have and it looks like they will also be missing two of their best overseas players in Kostas Sloukas and Tyler Dorsey, but Greece's chance to grab a gold medal is certainly greater than zero.\", \"from\": 7206, \"to\": 7450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7242, \"end\": 7245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0288350946681754e-56, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 7345, \"end\": 7359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Sloukas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kostas Sloukas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Sloukas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Sloukas\"}, {\"begin\": 7364, \"end\": 7376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Dorsey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tyler Dorsey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Dorsey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyler_Dorsey\"}, {\"begin\": 7382, \"end\": 7388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999023220939736, \"rank\": 9.768744794159763e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under new head coach Vassilis Spanoulis, who starred for Greece the last time they were in theOlympicsfor basketball in 2008, the Greeks rolled over their opponents at the Olympic qualifying tournament.\", \"from\": 7452, \"to\": 7654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7473, \"end\": 7491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vassilis_Spanoulis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vassilis Spanoulis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vassilis_Spanoulis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vassilis_Spanoulis\"}, {\"begin\": 7509, \"end\": 7515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999023220939736, \"rank\": 9.768744794159763e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7582, \"end\": 7588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 4.0211384312092925e-12, \"text\": \"Greeks\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most impressive was their lockdown defense, especially against Luka Doncic and Serbia.\", \"from\": 7655, \"to\": 7741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7718, \"end\": 7729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luka_Don\\u010di\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9999999939464033, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luka Doncic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luka_Don\\u010di\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luka_Don\\u010di\\u0107\"}, {\"begin\": 7734, \"end\": 7740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9374100470996596, \"rank\": 0.06676902289838449, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Giannis may be their only player on an NBA roster but their five-man group of Thomas Walkup, Nick Calathes, Kostas Papanikolaou, Giannis, and Georgios Papagiannis is an elite defensive group.\", \"from\": 7742, \"to\": 7933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7781, \"end\": 7784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0288350946681754e-56, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 7820, \"end\": 7833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Walkup\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\"}, {\"begin\": 7835, \"end\": 7848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Calathes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nick Calathes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Calathes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Calathes\"}, {\"begin\": 7850, \"end\": 7869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Papanikolaou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kostas Papanikolaou\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Papanikolaou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Papanikolaou\"}, {\"begin\": 7884, \"end\": 7904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Papagiannis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Georgios Papagiannis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Papagiannis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgios_Papagiannis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no one to pick on, and the size combination of Papagiannis and Giannis lets them defend the rim very well.\", \"from\": 7934, \"to\": 8049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Offense will be a conundrum for this team.\", \"from\": 8051, \"to\": 8093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Walkup and Calathes are not shooters, nor do they have a scoring mentality at all.\", \"from\": 8094, \"to\": 8176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Neither does Papanikolaou.\", \"from\": 8177, \"to\": 8203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They will need to be comfortable letting it fly regardless as teams swarm and surround Giannis, which will be the strategy every opponent deploys against them.\", \"from\": 8204, \"to\": 8363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With a lot of shooting luck, Greece could have enough could beat some of this tournament's best teams on the right day.\", \"from\": 8364, \"to\": 8483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8393, \"end\": 8399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999023220939736, \"rank\": 9.768744794159763e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greece will play their opening game against Canada on Saturday, July 27.\", \"from\": 8485, \"to\": 8557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8485, \"end\": 8491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999023220939736, \"rank\": 9.768744794159763e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8529, \"end\": 8535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6643726021527911, \"rank\": 0.35105792818989034, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will also face Australia and Spain in the group phase.\", \"from\": 8558, \"to\": 8617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8578, \"end\": 8587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5578130601866172, \"rank\": 0.7903687184652642, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8592, \"end\": 8597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.353943375634934e-18, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026Minute Media-All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 8619, \"to\": 8659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 8660, \"to\": 8736, \"en